assets.name: assets/4N6ZKjbW4J5
assets.description: My first project, a fantasy environment with some very obvious Rene Laloux borrowing. It features three safe houses, three deities, an array of characters and lots if hidden details. Shove your head into any solid object, there is often something inside. This was drawn in the early days of Tiltbrush so I was unable to scale up to draw tiny things and I had to stand on a chair to draw the large monster. This was also as large an area as was possible at that time.

Just in time for #ValentinesDay, a remake of the famous "Psyche Revived by Cupid's Kiss"

View in VR: https://poly.google.com/view/eMjclsLhBgG

Watch the live stream creation: https://www.twitch.tv/videos/227095094

Follow me at SwanVR.Art or @swanvrart

Thanks for viewing! ^^
